Package com.essbase.api.session

Interface Summary
IEssbase The IEssbase represent client sessions with the Essbase.
IEssLocationInfo The IEssLocationInfo provides location information about a running enterprise server instance.
IEssSession The IEssSession contains information about a signed on user session in EDS server.
 

Class Summary

IEssbase.EEssOrbPluginType The EEssOrbPluginType is an enumeration of supported ORB plug-in types.
